CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 28, 1962, pg. A3, reads: "Easter Worshippers Add Frills to Faith - Rodman Street - Following morning worship services at Rodman Street Baptist Church, parishioners adorned in Easter finery exchange 'season's greetings.' All Photos by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Crowd of women and men gathered on sidewalk in front of Rodman Street Baptist Church after Easter services, East Liberty
